  "summaries": [
    {
      "actionDate": "2026-03-16",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Grocery, Farm, and Food Worker Stabilization Grant Program Act of 2026</strong></p><p>This bill directs the Agricultural Marketing Service (AMS) to establish a grant program to provide&nbsp;farmworkers, meat processing workers, and grocery workers stabilization payments in the case of a natural disaster or other disaster. Specifically, AMS must provide funding to membership organizations or labor unions representing farmworkers, meat processing workers, and grocery workers for the payments.&nbsp;</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-04-03T15:02:23Z",
      "versionCode": "00"
    }
  ]
